-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fbo1665702879306.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fbo1665702879306.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fbo1665702879306.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fbo1665702879306\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Default Assignment Files\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__default_assignment_files_97652\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Default assignment files for Uniface products and servers are automatically created when you install Uniface.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__p_d29963e1_d29964e1_d29965e1\">Assignment files that are common to several Uniface products and servers are located in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">/common/adm</span> subdirectory of the installation. Assignment files that are specific to a Uniface product are located in the product's <span class=\"ph filepath\">/adm</span> subdirectory.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__p_d29966e1_d29967e1_d29968e1\">The following assignment files are used by Uniface:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Default Assignment Files</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n Assignment File\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n Default Location\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">dbms.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/common</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Configures the database connector, logon path, and options\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/common</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used by all Uniface applications.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/common</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used by the Uniface Router\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">urmon.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/common</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used by the Uniface Router Monitor\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used by the Uniface IDE\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">userver.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used the Uniface Server\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used by the Uniface Web Application Server\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">usyschr.asn</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbo1665702879306__table_d3098e1_d3099e1_d3100e1__entry__3\">\n Used by all Uniface applications running in character mode.\n <p class=\"p\">Not created on iSeries.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbo1665702879306__p_d29969e1_d29970e1_d29971e1\">On iSeries, assignment files are created in the installation library, as separate members in file <span class=\"ph filepath\">ASN</span>.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rvm1665703533449.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>dbms.asn</a><p>The dbms.asn file is a basic assignment file containing the DBMS assignment settings.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clr1665703536847.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>usys.asn</a><p>Every Uniface application looks for global assignments in a file called usys.asn in the USYSADM: (/adm) subdirectory of the Uniface installation directory.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrd1665702718309.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>urouter.asn</a><p>Assignment file for the Uniface Router. You can use the urouter.asn file to specify settings, paths to connectors, and Uniface Server environment definitions, such as USTs.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xvc1665702739627.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>urmon.asn</a><p>Assignment file for the Uniface Router Monitor. You can use the urmon.asn file to specify settings that relate to the Uniface Router Monitor.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ahf1665702750957.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>wasv.asn</a><p>The wasv.asn file is a basic assignment file for the Web Application Server.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyr1665702739836.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>usyschr.asn</a><p>The usyschr.asn file contains default widget settings for the character mode interface.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527431\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527431\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Default Assignment Files Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Default Assignment Files Default assignment files for Uniface products and servers are automatically created when you install Uniface. Assignment files that are common to several Uniface products and servers are located in the /common/adm subdirectory of the installation. Assignment files that are specific to a Uniface product are located in the product's /adm subdirectory. The following assignment files are used by Uniface: Table 1. Default Assignment Files Assignment File Default Location Description dbms.asn /common Configures the database connector, logon path, and options usys.asn /common Used by all Uniface applications. urouter.asn /common Used by the Uniface Router urmon.asn /common Used by the Uniface Router Monitor ide.asn /uniface Used by the Uniface IDE userver.asn /uniface Used the Uniface Server wasv.asn /uniface Used by the Uniface Web Application Server usyschr.asn /uniface Used by all Uniface applications running in character mode. Not created on iSeries. On iSeries, assignment files are created in the installation library, as separate members in file ASN . Related Links dbms.asn The dbms.asn file is a basic assignment file containing the DBMS assignment settings. usys.asn Every Uniface application looks for global assignments in a file called usys.asn in the USYSADM: (/adm) subdirectory of the Uniface installation directory. urouter.asn Assignment file for the Uniface Router. You can use the urouter.asn file to specify settings, paths to connectors, and Uniface Server environment definitions, such as USTs. urmon.asn Assignment file for the Uniface Router Monitor. You can use the urmon.asn file to specify settings that relate to the Uniface Router Monitor. wasv.asn The wasv.asn file is a basic assignment file for the Web Application Server. usyschr.asn The usyschr.asn file contains default widget settings for the character mode interface. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}